=== Test 1: CoalescingMergeTree Basic Tuple ===
Coalescing Basic - with FINAL:
1	(100,60,'updated')
2	(250,80,'second')
Coalescing Basic - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(100,60,'updated')
2	(250,80,'second')
=== Test 2: CoalescingMergeTree Nested Tuple ===
Coalescing Nested Tuple - with FINAL:
1	(100,(210,(300)))
2	(160,(250,(360)))
Coalescing Nested Tuple - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(100,(210,(300)))
2	(160,(250,(360)))
=== Test 3: CoalescingMergeTree Tuple before sorting key ===
Tuple before sort key - with FINAL:
1	(100,(210))
2	(160,(250))
Tuple before sort key - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(100,(210))
2	(160,(250))
=== Test 4: Explicit column_names_to_sum with nested Tuple ===
Explicit nested col - with FINAL:
1	(10,(50,30))	(100,200)	1000
2	(8,(6,10))	(50,60)	500
Explicit nested col - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(10,(50,30))	(100,200)	1000
2	(8,(6,10))	(50,60)	500
=== Test 5: Explicit column_names_to_sum - only specified Tuple is coalesced ===
Explicit mixed - with FINAL:
1	(10,40)	(100,200)	1000
2	(7,6)	(50,60)	500
Explicit mixed - after OPTIMIZE (not_coalesced keeps first value):
1	(10,40)	(100,200)	1000
2	(7,6)	(50,60)	500
